title: Gymboree: 20% Off Entire Purchase + Free Shipping = Girl’s Dresses ONLY $5.19 Shipped & MORE
text:
Now through February 12th, head on over to Gymboree.com where they are offering up FREE shipping on any order – no minimum and no promo code needed! Plus, they’re having a Everything Made for Play $2.99 & Up Sale as well as Clearance items starting at just 99¢ (sort Low to High)!
Even sweeter, through tomorrow only, you can use promo code SHUTTERFLY at checkout to score an extra 20% off your entire purchase ! Note that you will need to enter your address and information to add the promo code and then your discount will be reflected on the right side of the page.
Here are a few of the deals I spotted… Girl’s Navy French Terry Dress in Navy Medallion $6.49 (reg. $29.95)
ONLY $5.19 shipped with code SHUTTERFLY 
Toddler Girl’s Striped Shift Dress $6.49 (reg. $29.95)
ONLY $5.19 shipped with code SHUTTERFLY 

Toddler Boy’s Forest Stripe Hoodie $7.79 (reg. $32.95)
ONLY $6.23 shipped with code SHUTTERFLY 
…and MUCH more! 
(Thanks, Lesley!)
